and if this were the measure and practice of the difficulty the great difficulty of being an ascetic or Brahmin it would not be right to say It is hard to be an ascetic it is hard to be a Brahmin
because any householder or householders son  even the slavegirl who draws water  could do this saying Well I will go naked
That is the perfection of morality He guards the sensedoors etc
