Here a bhikkhu sees the eye as nonself he sees forms as nonself he sees eyeconsciousness as nonself he sees eyecontact as nonself he sees as nonself whatever feeling arises with eyecontact as condition whether pleasant or painful or neitherpainfulnorpleasant
Thisbhikkhus is the way that is suitable for attaining Nibbana
