And having said that he said further
he sat down at one side and said to the Blessed One Venerable sir as I understand the Dhamma taught by the Blessed One it is not easy while living in a home to lead the holy life utterly perfect and pure as a polished shell
Even in case of your death we would lose you unwillingly
so how could we give you our permission to go forth from the home life into homelessness while you are still living 
